# GlowCart Mobile App Design

## Project Overview
GlowCart is a mobile beauty shopping application designed using Figma as part of a Mobile App Wireframing project.

The project focuses on UI/UX design, user flow creation, low-fidelity wireframes, and prototype development.

## Features
- Splash Screen
- Login Screen
- Password Screen
- Product Search Screen
- Product Categories
- Prototype Navigation

## User Flow
Splash Screen → Login → Password → Search Page

## Tools Used
- Figma
- GitHub

## Project Screens
1. Splash Screen
2. Login Screen
3. Password Screen
4. Search Screen

## Objective
To understand mobile app planning, user flow creation, and wireframe development using Figma.

